POST /seats/lock

POST /seats/book

EVENTS

GET /events

POST /events (admin)

RESTAURANTS

GET /restaurants

POST /restaurants (admin)

BOOKINGS

POST /booking/create

GET /booking/history

PAYMENTS

POST /payment/create

POST /payment/verify

